high_descs: Walk forward to the wall then turn right to face the left end of the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn left to face the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Turn left and walk forward and turn right to face the stove.
Place the tomato in the pan on the front of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the right to face the fridge.
Place the pan with a tomato slice in it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To place a pan with a tomato slice in it in the fridge.

high_descs: Move forward and face the white table to your right.
Take the knife from the white table in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter by the stove on your left.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Place the knife on the counter in front of you.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the stove on your right.
Place the tomato in the pan on the stove in front of you.
Take the pan with the tomato from the stove in front of you.
Turn right and face the fridge on your left.
Place the pan with the tomato in the fridge in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice in a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: go forward, turn right and go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn right, go forward, turn right
Slice the tomato on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Pick up a tomato slice from the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn right in front of the stove
Put the tomato slice into the pan
Pick up the pan from the stove
Turn left, go forward, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, put a slice in a pan, put the pan to the fridge
